PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1990-2441 of November 16, 1990 respecting the appointment of Jean-Pierre Gaboury, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Ottawa/Atlantic Regional Office); and designation of the said Jean-Pierre Gaboury as Assistant Deputy Chairperson of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Ottawa/Atlantic Regional Office) for a term ending January 17, 1996.
